Alice Nielsen https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Alice_Nielsen 0 Alice Nielsen (June 7, 1872 – March 8, 1943) was a Broadway performer and operatic soprano who had her own opera company and starred in several Victor Herbert operettas.
